Starscream passed over the flames and look down at the mouse, movin 
and twitching. It was still alive, and Starscream did not have it in 
him to fight a helpless bot. He watched the fire on her die down, and 
than placed her in the cockpit and sealed it tight, chaining her to 
the seat. He would take her back to KitKat, and she would decide what 
to do with her. Maybe she knew where Megatron was. He would stop by 
the base, put this rodent in custody, and than go and help Drillbit 
defeat Inferno. He blasted of towards the base.
